{"tid":2327521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔真係做到野：承認非禮兩名非華裔女童等控罪 龍緯汶被判囚32個月","createTime":"2020-12-16T06:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T07:04:00.000Z","uid":71166,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"219a6778de5f978f359258aa756993624eff5f41","tid":2327521,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:15:14.000Z","msg":"46歲南方民主同盟主席龍緯汶承認屢次非禮兩名非華裔女童，拍攝她們私處照片等，在區域法院被判入獄32月。<br />\n<br />\n龍緯汶上月已承認共7項控罪，包括在2017年至2018年期間，曾在游泳池更衣室內，猥褻侵犯當時只有6歲的女童，並於今年3月及和4月，在旺角塘尾道永利工業大廈一單位內再兩度非禮她。<br />\n<br />\n他又另外被控曾在荃灣住所內向當時3歲的女童，作出嚴重猥褻行為，使用電話製作一段有兒童色情的錄影片段，龍緯汶在住所管有19張兒童色情照片和一段兒童色情影片等兒童色情物品。<br />\n<br />\n年初唔係有連巴揭發，條友仲傷害緊D細路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FO72Mzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFO72Mzy.jpg&h=db592eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pqcx8NT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqcx8NT.jpg&h=b2e2306f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7qzCGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7qzCGh.jpg&h=2d15baa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnD9rzC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnD9rzC.jpg&h=7be8e0b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc5327173d3f58d6df3d137301869b0597a55939","tid":2327521,"uid":171506,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:20:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔罕有做實事<br />\n當年邊個出post踢爆，要表揚下"},{"pid":"861e55b416436b2a815bfbcd92219de583d4ddfe","tid":2327521,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:21:33.000Z","msg":"咁矮"},{"pid":"c031158aaa915d99d35bb49b1cf81b77cb662a4d","tid":2327521,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc5327173d3f58d6df3d137301869b0597a55939","tid":2327